    {
        "content": "<p>What do you want to do exactly? If you want to prove that the derivative of 1/ax at x (not zero) exists and is is what it should be, then this will be the statement of your lemma (stated in terms of <code>HasDerivAt</code>) and the proof will involve lemmas like the ones I mentioned or very similar ones. If you want Lean to compute the derivative for you, AFAIK it won't and you will end up being very disappointed ...</p>",
